                        <placeName ref="#aphtetrastoon">Tetrastoon</placeName>, <placeName type="monuList" ref="#aphtetrastoonw">West portico</placeName>: A round plinth, on which this stone probably stood, is apparently in its original position, against the west portico, just south of <ref type="inscription" n="62" target="iAph080410"/> and<ref type="iAph" n="065" target=".xml"/>. .</origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="0361" notAfter="0363" evidence="reign">A.D. 361/363</origDate>
                  </origin>
