         <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" source="#ala2004">
            <p>To Good Fortune. Antonius Tatianos, <foreign xml:lang="la">clarissimus praeses</foreign>, having built all the work of the tetrastoon 
               that can be seen from the foundations, and all the surrounding decoration, for the metropolis, <supplied reason="subaudible">set up this statue</supplied> 
               of Flavius Claudius <supplied reason="omitted">Julianus</supplied> <add>Theodosius</add> , the eternal and most pious Augustus.</p>
         </div>
